Police in Nelson Mandela Bay have appealed to the public for assistance in an investigation linked to a missing vehicle. According to police, a retailer at Moffet on Main shopping centre in Walmer discovered that her white Mercedes-Benz was missing from the parking area on March 27. This shortly after she noticed that her keys were missing. CCTV footage indicated that these two people can assist in the investigation of the missing vehicle. &nbsp; Picture: Supplied Picture: Supplied Anyone with any information regarding their whereabouts can phone Warrant Officer Jaco Botes on 071-671-1243. Related Share on Facebook Share Share on Twitter Tweet Share on Google Plus Share